- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper deals with area coverage problems for nonlinear robotic systems.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper presents a control policy for multiagent systems with nonlinear dynamics.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with developing a closed-form controller for area coverage problems.
- cs.GT (Game Theory) is mentioned in the abstract as the paper provides an analysis on ergodic policies as a Nash equilibrium for game theoretic applications.
